u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">Ἡσύχιος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ζήσα[ς\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἠγορήσατο\">ἠγορ]ήσατο\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"αὐτο\">αὐτο[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-text=\"πάντα\">πάντα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"τ\">τ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"υτα\">υτα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"οὖν\">οὖν\u003C/span> Σ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΓΙΑ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Ῥ\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μητέρα\">...]ΕΡΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μου\">ΜΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">IΟΥΦΙΝ.[.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">ΗΣΥΧΙΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ΖΗΣΑ[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἠγορήσατο\">....]ΗΣΑΤΟ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"αὐτο\">ΑΥΤΟ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"πάντα\">ΠΑΝΤΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τ\">Τ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"υτα\">ΥΤΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"οὖν\">ΟΥΝ\u003C/span>Σ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΓΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Ῥ\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003291_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003291_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003291.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003291-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>lapis: ΙΟΥΦΙΝ; Korhonen: ουφῖν[αν]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Korhonen: ζήσα[ς]; Pleket: ζήσα[σαν]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 3\">line.3: \u003Cspan>Korhonen: [ἠγορ]ήσατο\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 4\">line.4: \u003Cspan>Korhonen reads a Σ, but it could also be a Ο\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 5\">line.5: \u003Cspan>Korhonen reads a Γ, but it could also be a T\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>…my mother Rouphinan … Hesychios, while alive, purchased … all …\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… mia madre Rouphinan … Hesychios, mentre era vivo, acquistò … tutto …\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph must have been partly metrical (ll. 1-2), as Korhonen pointed out. It can be assumed that Hesychios had acquired the burial place while alive (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ζήσας\u003C/span>) for his mother Rouphina (for himself and another deceased (?): \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">αὐτοῖς\u003C/span>). At l. 4 a supplement could be \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[πάντα τ]ὸν χρόνον\u003C/span> to indicate the permanent possession of the purchase of the tomb or with \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[πάντα τ]ὸν τόπον\u003C/span> to indicate the purchase of the entire place for the burial of the deceased. The names Rouphina and Hesychios recur in Christian epitaphs from Syracuse, see SEG 36.872 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002932\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002932\u003C/a>, IG 14.164 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000985\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000985\u003C/a>, Agnello 1950: 60 no.11 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002918\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002918\u003C/a>. \u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 2004.0655 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 54.0910 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 194 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>A with broken bar, lunate Ε and Σ, curved Υ, Φ with a small bowl and extended upright.\u003C/p> Lines 1-6  12-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[228,231,234,237,240,242,245,248,251],{"id":229,"html":230},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μητέρα\">μητ]έρα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μου\">μου\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">&lt;Ῥ&gt;ουφῖνα̣[ν\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">Ἡσύχιος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ζήσα[ς\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἠγορήσατο\">ἠγορ]ήσατο\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"αὐτο\">αὐτο[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-text=\"πάντα\">πάντα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"τ\">τ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"υτα\">υτα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"οὖν\">οὖν\u003C/span> Σ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΓΙΑ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Ῥ\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μητέρα\">...]ΕΡΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μου\">ΜΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">IΟΥΦΙΝ.[.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">ΗΣΥΧΙΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ΖΗΣΑ[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἠγορήσατο\">....]ΗΣΑΤΟ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"αὐτο\">ΑΥΤΟ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"πάντα\">ΠΑΝΤΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τ\">Τ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"υτα\">ΥΤΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"οὖν\">ΟΥΝ\u003C/span>Σ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΓΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Ῥ\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":232,"html":233},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003291_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003291_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003291.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003291-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":235,"html":236},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>lapis: ΙΟΥΦΙΝ; Korhonen: ουφῖν[αν]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Korhonen: ζήσα[ς]; Pleket: ζήσα[σαν]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 3\">line.3: \u003Cspan>Korhonen: [ἠγορ]ήσατο\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 4\">line.4: \u003Cspan>Korhonen reads a Σ, but it could also be a Ο\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 5\">line.5: \u003Cspan>Korhonen reads a Γ, but it could also be a T\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":238,"html":239},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>…my mother Rouphinan … Hesychios, while alive, purchased … all …\u003C/p>  ",{"id":238,"html":241},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… mia madre Rouphinan … Hesychios, mentre era vivo, acquistò … tutto …\u003C/p>  ",{"id":243,"html":244},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph must have been partly metrical (ll. 1-2), as Korhonen pointed out. It can be assumed that Hesychios had acquired the burial place while alive (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ζήσας\u003C/span>) for his mother Rouphina (for himself and another deceased (?): \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">αὐτοῖς\u003C/span>). At l. 4 a supplement could be \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[πάντα τ]ὸν χρόνον\u003C/span> to indicate the permanent possession of the purchase of the tomb or with \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[πάντα τ]ὸν τόπον\u003C/span> to indicate the purchase of the entire place for the burial of the deceased. The names Rouphina and Hesychios recur in Christian epitaphs from Syracuse, see SEG 36.872 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002932\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002932\u003C/a>, IG 14.164 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000985\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000985\u003C/a>, Agnello 1950: 60 no.11 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic002918\" target=\"_blank\">ISic002918\u003C/a>. \u003C/p>  ",{"id":246,"html":247},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 2004.0655 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 54.0910 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 194 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":249,"html":250},"handnote","\u003Cp>A with broken bar, lunate Ε and Σ, curved Υ, Φ with a small bowl and extended upright.\u003C/p> Lines 1-6  12-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":252,"html":253},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[255,257,260,261],{"html":256},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":258,"lang":125,"html":259},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μητέρα\">μητ]έρα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μου\">μου\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ῬIουφῖναν\">&lt;Ῥ&gt;ουφῖνα̣[ν\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡσύχιος\">Ἡσύχιος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · \u003Csp